              "2021-11-24 09:12:35.070 - INFO - Pass ✓... (test-basic-arithmetic / test-add): Add pass\n",
              "2021-11-24 09:12:35.080 - ERROR - Fail ✗... (test-basic-arithmetic / test-add): Add fail \n",
              "                                    Expected: 5\n",
              "                                    Got: 3\n",
              "2021-11-24 09:12:35.094 - INFO - Pass ✓... (test-basic-arithmetic / test-sub): Sub pass\n",
              "2021-11-24 09:12:35.103 - ERROR - Fail ✗... (test-basic-arithmetic / test-sub): Sub fail \n",
              "                                    Expected: 1\n",
              "                                    Got: -1\n",
              "2021-11-24 09:12:35.104 - DEBUG - (test-basic-arithmetic): Test Summary → Total: 5    Pass: 3    Fail: 2\n"
