           "source": [
            "(deffixture fix-c ((setv a 1)) (None))\n",
            "(deffixture fix-d ((setv b 1)) (None))\n",
            "\n",
            "(▶ (with-fixture fix-c \n",
            "    (▶ (with-fixture fix-d \n",
            "        (▶ (test-add-var))))))"
           ]
          },
          {
           "cell_type": "markdown",
           "id": "b43b6fec",
